    "decoded_text": "<CTRL_F4> hath woken up.<CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x60><CTRL_VARIABLE_STRING>Thou art dead.<CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>Thou art strong enough!<CTRL_VARIABLE_STRING>Why can thou not defeat the Dragonlord?'<CTRL_PAUSE_0_5S><CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>If thou art planning to take a rest, first see King Lorik<BYTE_0x52><CTRL_END_WAIT><CTRL_F8> held the Rainbow Drop toward the sky.<CTRL_VARIABLE_STRING><BYTE_0x60><CTRL_PAUSE_0_5S><CTRL_END_WAIT>But no rainbow appeared here.<CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>Good morning.<CTRL_VARIABLE_STRING>Thou hast had a good night<BYTE_0x53>s sleep I hope<BYTE_0x52><CTRL_PAUSE_0_5S><CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>I shall see thee again<BYTE_0x52><CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>Good morning.<CTRL_VARIABLE_STRING>Thou seems to have spent a good night<BYTE_0x52><CTRL_PAUSE_0_5S><CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>Good night<BYTE_0x52><CTRL_VARIABLE_STRING><CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>Okay.<CTRL_VARIABLE_STRING>Good-bye, traveler<BYTE_0x52><CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>Welcome to the traveler<BYTE_0x53>s Inn.<CTRL_VARIABLE_STRING>Room and board is <CTRL_GOLD_COST> GOLD per night.<CTRL_VARIABLE_STRING>Dost thou want a room?'<CTRL_VARIABLE_STRING><CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>All the best to thee<BYTE_0x52><CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>There are no stairs here<BYTE_0x52><CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>Thou cannot enter here<BYTE_0x52><CTRL_END_WAIT><BYTE_0x50>There is no one there<BYTE_0x52><CTRL_END_WAIT>"
